    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-inner">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <p class="overline">Free Miro Template</p>
                <h1>Run better retrospectives with a template your team will actually enjoy.</h1>
                <p class="hero-sub">RetroSprint gives your sprint retros structure and personality — three clear zones, a visual style that keeps energy up, and zero setup time.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="#cta" class="btn-primary">Get the Template</a>
                    <a href="#preview" class="btn-ghost">See preview</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="preview.png" alt="RetroSprint Miro Template showing three columns: What Went Well, To Improve, and Action Items">
            </div>
        </div>
