                    </div>
                    <h3>One-click import</h3>
                    <p>Open the link, hit "Use template", and you're running. No plugins, no config.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Three clear zones</h3>
                    <p>Pre-built columns for <strong>What Went Well</strong>, <strong>To Improve</strong>, and <strong>Action Items</strong>.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Voting built in</h3>
                    <p>Dot-voting areas so your team can prioritize what matters without extra tooling.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Works for any team</h3>
                    <p>Remote, hybrid, or co-located — everyone sees the same board in real time.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg>
