                    <p class="overline">Template Preview</p>
                    <h2>See what your retro will look like.</h2>
                    <p>Three color-coded columns on a dark canvas. Sticky notes that are easy to scan. A layout that naturally guides conversation from celebration to action.</p>
                    <ul class="check-list">
                        <li>
                            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                            Color-coded sticky notes per zone
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
